comments: I panicked at first because I was trying a lot of different ways to remember them. I started relating the words to things I was already familiar with to help them stick, for example, Zetithou sounds a lot like a character from Demon Slayer! Buviso was the first to stick because I attached it to the colour, it's like bloom - pink - buviso. After that, I would hear the word but when I needed to type it out, I would do it phonetically in English; Wop-i-f-u instead of the alien language pronunciation. The th and f would always make an s sound
